Enjoy your favourite movies, music and photos with the Logik L1DVDB20 DVD Player. It plays DVDs, CDs, and has a USB port, so you can plug in and play from a flash drive.And with a remote included, you can control your entertainment from the comfort of your sofa.

Connect your AV equipment reliably with the 1 m Essential C1SCT15 SCART Cable. It's great for older AV equipment such as retro games consoles, DVD players, VCRs and certain TV models. You'll enjoy a solid, reliable connection and clear signal transfer thanks to its nickel-plated connectors. Dual-layer shielding ensures minimal interference so you can make the most of your entertainment.
